Hillery Beachey  at Dominguez Field, January 19-28 1912  The third air meet held at Dominguez  -( LA area). engine Roberts 4-X  Double ailerons worked down only
Hillery Beachey  born May 9,1885 Boise, Idaho  Died  July 22,1964 California State Hospital
Flew for Aero Club of America license # 89 January 10,1912  Kinloch Field near St. Louis , Missouri  license granted one week later January 17,1912
